
CSS Animation

Learned how to create animations using the "@keyframes" rule.

.box{
    width:100px;
    height:100px;
    background:blue;
    animation:move 3s infinite;
}

@keyframes move{
    from{
        transform:translateX(0);
    }
    to{
        transform:translateX(300px);
    }
}

