CSS Transform

Practiced different transform functions.

.box{
    transform:rotate(45deg);
}

.box{
    transform:scale(1.5);
}

.box{
    transform:translate(100px,50px);
}

.box{
    transform:skew(20deg,10deg);
}

---

CSS Transition

Applied smooth transition effects on hover.

button{
    background:green;
    color:white;
    padding:10px;
    transition:0.5s;
}

button:hover{
    background:red;
    transform:scale(1.2);
}

---

CSS Selectors

Universal Selector

*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
}

Element Selector

p{
    color:blue;
}

Class Selector

.text{
    color:red;
}

ID Selector

#heading{
    color:green;
}

Group Selector

h1, p{
    color:purple;
}

Descendant Selector

div p{
    color:orange;
}

Child Selector

div > p{
    color:brown;
}

Adjacent Sibling Selector

h1 + p{
    color:red;
}

General Sibling Selector

h1 ~ p{
    color:blue;
}

Attribute Selector

input[type="text"]{
    border:2px solid black;
}

Pseudo-class Selector

button:hover{
    background:black;
    color:white;
}

Pseudo-element Selector

p::first-letter{
    font-size:30px;
    color:red;
}
